name: Hasbulla's Chicken
description: The project is a meme coin named after the famous celebrity Hasbulla's pet Chicken, which was named after Conor McGregor when they had a fight. The meme is one of Hasbulla's beloved pets and is the first meme of its kind. The story of Hasbulla naming his chicken has gained international attention and was even posted in The Sun and other major new-papers. Its a really great story and we have a great meme and community
